Name: Nippon Ecchi Jigsaw
About the game: Introduction: Nippon Ecchi Jigsaw is simple puzzle jigsaw game. Game first version contains over 10 different anime/ecchi style images. Some have no mature content and some image have more mature content, like boobs. Use just mouse and drag&drop jigsaw pieces and try to solve every images. There are 6 different puzzle sizes. Features: - Only basic settings - Over 10 different images. - Anime girl and boys images
